'''第71屆金球獎（71st Golden Globe Awards）'''在2014年1月12日於美国[[加州|加州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[比佛利山_(加利福尼亞州)|比佛利山]]比華利希爾頓酒店舉行頒獎典禮，由[[NBC|NBC]]進行電視轉播，用以表掦2013年出色的電影及電視作品<ref>[http://www.apdnews.com/news/61233.html 金球奖获奖名单出炉] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116081448/http://www.apdnews.com/news/61233.html |date=2014-01-16 }}，亚太日报，2014年1月14日</ref>。頒獎典禮由[[Dick_Clark_Productions|Dick Clark Productions]]及[[荷里活外國記者協會|荷里活外國記者協會]]（HFPA）合辦，<ref name=GGAnnouncement>{{cite web|url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/timetable71/|title=The Hollywood Foreign Press Association and Producer Dick Clark Productions Bring 'The 71st Annual Golden Globe Awards' Live Coast-To-Coast On NBC Sunday, January 12, 2014|date=2013-04-18|work=goldenglobes.org|accessdate=2013-10-10|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014073456/http://www.goldenglobes.org/timetable71/|dead-url=no}}</ref>兩名女演員[[蒂娜·菲|蒂娜·菲]]和[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]因在[[第70屆金球獎|上一年的颁奖典礼]]上受到欢迎而继续擔任主持人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tina-fey-amy-poehler-host-648283|title=Tina Fey, Amy Poehler to Host Golden Globes for Next Two Years|accessdate=2013-10-17|date=2013-10-15|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|author=Belloni, Matthew|archive-date=2014-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228053946/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tina-fey-amy-poehler-host-648283|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=t13globeslist>{{cite news|title=第71届金球奖完整获奖名单|url=http://cn.tmagazine.com/film-tv/20140113/t13globeslist/|accessdate=2014-01-14|newspaper=纽约时报国际生活中文版|date=2014-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114215248/http://cn.tmagazine.com/film-tv/20140113/t13globeslist/|archive-date=2014-01-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>提名名單在2013年12月12日由[[阿茲·安薩里|阿茲·安薩里]]、[[佐伊·索尔达娜|佐伊·索尔达娜]]和[[奧利維亞·魏爾德|奧利維亞·魏爾德]]公布。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-golden-globes-nominees-winners-complete-list,0,6845028.story#axzz2nHEfg9AW|title=Golden Globes nominations 2014: The complete list of nominees|date=2013-12-12|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2013-12-12|archive-date=2014-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140216235939/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-golden-globes-nominees-winners-complete-list,0,6845028.story#axzz2nHEfg9AW|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/film-news/10513775/Golden-Globes-nominations-2014-12-Years-a-Slave-and-American-Hustle-lead-way.html|title=Golden Globes nominations 2014: 12 Years a Slave and American Hustle lead way|date=2013-12-12|work=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2013-12-13|archive-date=2013-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216001817/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/film-news/10513775/Golden-Globes-nominations-2014-12-Years-a-Slave-and-American-Hustle-lead-way.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年9月13日，大會宣布[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]獲得本屆[[塞西尔·B·德米尔奖|塞西尔·B·德米尔奖]]（終身成就獎）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/golden-globes-woody-allen-receive-629107 |title=Golden Globes: Woody Allen to Receive Cecil B. DeMille Award |date=2013-09-13 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archive-date=2014-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109023735/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/golden-globes-woody-allen-receive-629107 |dead-url=no }}</ref>但[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]並未出席，由[[黛安·基頓|黛安·基頓]]代領。

